{% comment %}
  Joy: Referral Program Section (Style 1 - Horizontal Layout)

  A referral program section with side-by-side layout for image and form.
  Customers enter their email to generate a shareable referral link.

  Key Features:
    - Email form with auto-generation of referral links via Joy SDK
    - Horizontal layout: Image positioned beside form (left or right)
    - Auto-prefills email for logged-in customers
    - Social sharing: Copy link, email, Facebook, WhatsApp
    - LocalStorage caching: Saves referral data for 30 days
    - Success stats: Shows count of friends who joined
    - Optional "Generate New Link" for guests
    - Responsive: Stacks vertically on mobile

  Customization (Theme Editor):
    - Layout: Container width, full-width mode, border radius, inner padding
    - Image: Upload and position (left/right)
    - Content: Badge, title, description, terms text
    - Form: Email placeholder, button texts (default, loading, error)
    - Sharing: Toggle copy/email/Facebook/WhatsApp buttons, share texts
    - Colors: Section background, card, button, text, inputs
    - Typography: Font sizes for badge, title, description, form
    - Spacing: Section padding (top/bottom)

  Use Cases:
    - Dedicated referral page
    - Account page referral widget
    - Loyalty program landing page

  Difference from Style 2:
    - Style 1: Horizontal layout with image beside form
    - Style 2: Overlay card layout with background image
{% endcomment %}

